data.description: Been dreaming of small-town Texas living but still being close enough to be about an hour from Dallas? Dreaming of a unique home filled with character and charm? Dreaming of exposed brick, shiplap, original hardwoods, mahogany doors but with a MODERN kitchen, SPECTACULAR primary suite and UPDATED bathrooms? Well, your dreams are about to come true! This 4401 sq ft Craftsman-style home was built in 1910 and offers 5 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms plus a half bath, office, huge kitchen, dining room, living room as well as a wraparound front porch! The quarter-acre corner lot boasts parking on two sides, a roomy backyard and party barn with storage. The primary suite is on the main level and has TWO bathrooms, a HUGE walk-in closet and a PRIVATE study with direct access to the porch. The modern farmhouse kitchen is a chef's delight with walk-in pantry and coffee bar! Located in booming Bonham, Texas minutes from the NEW Bois D'Arc Lake! Would also make an AWESOME vacation rental! Don't wait!
